Upon rousing themselves from hyper-sleep, Payton 
(Dennis Quaid) and Bower (Ben Foster), a pair of 
crewmen assigned to work on a spacecraft, discover 
startling gaps in their collective memory -- including 
who they are and what, exactly, their mission was in 
the first place. The plot thickens when they realize 
they're not the only ones on board the ship. Cam 
Gigandet co-stars in this gripping sci-fi thriller.

Starring: Dennis Quaid, Ben Foster
